title: Tar Devils Sociology Symposium
text:
Welcome to the Tar Devils Sociology Symposium webpage!
The second Tar Devils Sociology Symposium will be held February 1, 2026, at UNC Chapel Hill. It will bring together the graduate student researchers at the University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill and Duke University.
